snippet.title: Who Shuffled My Shapes? Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Who Shuffled My Shapes is a brand new puzzle game, available on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1868060

A staggering 20 different puzzles for you to play with. 
With puzzle shapes ranging from classic cubes to pyramids, dodecahedrons, and even off-axis shapes; there is something exciting for uninitiated and expert puzzlers alike!

Coming July 2022!
